{
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "verse_number": 1,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:1",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ",
      "translation": "1. J’en jure par le Jour de la Résurrection !",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "verse_number": 2,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:2",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلنَّفۡسِ ٱللَّوَّامَةِ",
      "translation": "2. J’en jure par l’âme prompte à se blâmer !",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "verse_number": 3,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:3",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَلَّن نَّجۡمَعَ عِظَامَهُۥ",
      "translation": "3. L’homme s’imagine-t-il que Nous ne rassemblerons pas ses os ?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "verse_number": 4,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:4",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "بَلَىٰ قَٰدِرِينَ عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّسَوِّيَ بَنَانَهُۥ",
      "translation": "4. Que si ! Nous sommes Capable même de reconstituer tel quel le bout de ses doigts.[587]",
      "footnotes": "[587] De toutes les parties du corps, Allah cite ici le bout des doigts comme étant les plus difficiles à refaire. Pourquoi ? L’allusion aux empreintes digitales est évidente. La science contemporaine a démontré que même le clonage ne donnerait pas des empreintes digitales identiques."
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "verse_number": 5,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:5",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "بَلۡ يُرِيدُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ لِيَفۡجُرَ أَمَامَهُۥ",
      "translation": "5. L’homme préfèrerait poursuivre sa vie en rebelle et pervers.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "verse_number": 6,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:6",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَسۡـَٔلُ أَيَّانَ يَوۡمُ ٱلۡقِيَٰمَةِ",
      "translation": "6. Il demande : « À quand donc le Jour de la Résurrection ? »",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "verse_number": 7,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:7",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَإِذَا بَرِقَ ٱلۡبَصَرُ",
      "translation": "7. Puis lorsque l’œil sera hagard,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "verse_number": 8,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:8",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَخَسَفَ ٱلۡقَمَرُ",
      "translation": "8. et que la lune se sera éclipsée,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "verse_number": 9,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:9",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَجُمِعَ ٱلشَّمۡسُ وَٱلۡقَمَرُ",
      "translation": "9. et que le soleil et la lune auront été réunis,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "verse_number": 10,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:10",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَقُولُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذٍ أَيۡنَ ٱلۡمَفَرُّ",
      "translation": "10. l’homme dira, ce jour-là : « Où fuir ? »",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "verse_number": 11,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:11",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّا لَا وَزَرَ",
      "translation": "11. Non ! Il n’y aura point d’issue.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "verse_number": 12,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:12",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمُسۡتَقَرُّ",
      "translation": "12. C’est vers ton Seigneur que, ce jour-là, sera l’aboutissement.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "verse_number": 13,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:13",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يُنَبَّؤُاْ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بِمَا قَدَّمَ وَأَخَّرَ",
      "translation": "13. Et ce jour-là, l’homme sera informé de ce qu’il aura avancé (comme acte) et de ce qu’il aura renvoyé à plus tard.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "verse_number": 14,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:14",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "بَلِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ عَلَىٰ نَفۡسِهِۦ بَصِيرَةٞ",
      "translation": "14. L’homme se dressera plutôt contre lui-même en témoin oculaire,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "verse_number": 15,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:15",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَلَوۡ أَلۡقَىٰ مَعَاذِيرَهُۥ",
      "translation": "15. quand bien même il invoquerait ses excuses.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "verse_number": 16,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:16",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَا تُحَرِّكۡ بِهِۦ لِسَانَكَ لِتَعۡجَلَ بِهِۦٓ",
      "translation": "16. Ne le[588] tourne pas (plusieurs fois) dans ta langue, pressé que tu es de le retenir.",
      "footnotes": "[588] Le Coran. La parole est ici adressée à Muhammad (paix et bénédiction d’Allah sur lui)."
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "verse_number": 17,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:17",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا جَمۡعَهُۥ وَقُرۡءَانَهُۥ",
      "translation": "17. C’est à Nous qu’il appartient de le rassembler (dans ton cœur et ta mémoire) et de te le faire lire.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "verse_number": 18,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:18",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَإِذَا قَرَأۡنَٰهُ فَٱتَّبِعۡ قُرۡءَانَهُۥ",
      "translation": "18. Lorsque Nous le lisons, suis-en la lecture.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "verse_number": 19,
      "page_number": 577,
      "verse_key": "75:19",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا بَيَانَهُۥ",
      "translation": "19. Puis il Nous appartient de l’expliquer.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "verse_number": 20,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:20",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّا بَلۡ تُحِبُّونَ ٱلۡعَاجِلَةَ",
      "translation": "20. Non, vous aimez plutôt la vie fugace.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "verse_number": 21,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:21",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَتَذَرُونَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةَ",
      "translation": "21. Et vous négligez la vie de l’autre monde.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "verse_number": 22,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:22",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاضِرَةٌ",
      "translation": "22. Ce jour-là, des visages seront épanouis,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "verse_number": 23,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:23",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَىٰ رَبِّهَا نَاظِرَةٞ",
      "translation": "23. qui contempleront leur Seigneur.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "verse_number": 24,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:24",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذِۭ بَاسِرَةٞ",
      "translation": "24. Et ce jour-là, (d’autres) visages seront livides,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "verse_number": 25,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:25",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تَظُنُّ أَن يُفۡعَلَ بِهَا فَاقِرَةٞ",
      "translation": "25. S’attendant à courir un terrible péril.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "verse_number": 26,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:26",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّآ إِذَا بَلَغَتِ ٱلتَّرَاقِيَ",
      "translation": "26. Non ! Quand (l’âme à l’agonie) aura atteint les clavicules,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "verse_number": 27,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:27",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَقِيلَ مَنۡۜ رَاقٖ",
      "translation": "27. et qu’il sera demandé : « Quel exorciste (peut la sauver) ? »",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "verse_number": 28,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:28",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَظَنَّ أَنَّهُ ٱلۡفِرَاقُ",
      "translation": "28. et que (l’agonisant) aura réalisé que le moment de la séparation est arrivé,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "verse_number": 29,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:29",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلۡتَفَّتِ ٱلسَّاقُ بِٱلسَّاقِ",
      "translation": "29. et que ses deux jambes se seront croisées,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "verse_number": 30,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:30",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ يَوۡمَئِذٍ ٱلۡمَسَاقُ",
      "translation": "30. C’est vers ton Seigneur, alors, qu’il sera acheminé.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "verse_number": 31,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:31",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَلَا صَدَّقَ وَلَا صَلَّىٰ",
      "translation": "31. Il n’a ni cru ni prié,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "verse_number": 32,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:32",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَلَٰكِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ",
      "translation": "32. mais il a nié (le Message) et s’est détourné de la foi.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "verse_number": 33,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:33",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ ذَهَبَ إِلَىٰٓ أَهۡلِهِۦ يَتَمَطَّىٰٓ",
      "translation": "33. Puis il s’en est allé, fier et heureux, vers sa famille.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "verse_number": 34,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:34",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰ",
      "translation": "34. «Malheur à toi, sur malheur !",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "verse_number": 35,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:35",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ أَوۡلَىٰ لَكَ فَأَوۡلَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "35. Puis malheur à toi, sur malheur ! »",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "verse_number": 36,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:36",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَيَحۡسَبُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ أَن يُتۡرَكَ سُدًى",
      "translation": "36. L’homme s’imagine-il qu’il n’aura pas de compte à rendre ?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "verse_number": 37,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:37",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَلَمۡ يَكُ نُطۡفَةٗ مِّن مَّنِيّٖ يُمۡنَىٰ",
      "translation": "37. N’a-t-il pas été une simple goutte de sperme éjaculé,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "verse_number": 38,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:38",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ كَانَ عَلَقَةٗ فَخَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ",
      "translation": "38. puis une petite masse de sang coagulé qu’Allah a, par la suite, créée et façonnée ?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "verse_number": 39,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:39",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَجَعَلَ مِنۡهُ ٱلزَّوۡجَيۡنِ ٱلذَّكَرَ وَٱلۡأُنثَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "39. Il en a fait alors le couple : le mâle et la femelle.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "verse_number": 40,
      "page_number": 578,
      "verse_key": "75:40",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 58,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 231,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
